org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.json

Class JCrunProductDiscovery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.common.RunProductDiscovery
      • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.json.JCrunProductDiscovery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BridgeCommunicationProtocol, JsonBridgeCommunicationProtocol

    @NonNullByDefault
class JCrunProductDiscovery
extends RunProductDiscovery
implements JsonBridgeCommunicationProtocol
    Specific bridge communication message supported by the Velux bridge.

    Message semantic:Action to start discovery of products, i.e. Velux devices.

    It defines information how to send query and receive answer through the VeluxBridgeProvider as described by the JsonBridgeCommunicationProtocol.

    Author:
    Guenther Schreiner - Initial contribution.
